{
  "title": "环境",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<div style=\"word-wrap: break-word; -webkit-nbsp-mode: space; -webkit-line-break: after-white-space; white-space: normal;\"><div><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在CentOS5的时代，由于yum源中没有git，所以需要预先安装一系列的依赖包。但在CentOS6的yum源中已经有git的版本了，可以直接使用yum源进行安装。</p><div style=\"background: rgb(239, 255, 244); border: 0px solid rgb(147, 147, 147); padding: 10px 20px; overflow: auto; margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 14px; clear: both; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 14px;\">\n$ sudo yum install git\n</pre></div><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">但是yum源中安装的git版本是1.7.1，太老了，Github等需要的Git版本最低都不能低于1.7.2 。所以我们一般不用上面的方法。而是下载git源码，编译安装。</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">编译安装的步骤是【4】：</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（1）首先先更新系统</p><div style=\"background: rgb(239, 255, 244); border: 0px solid rgb(147, 147, 147); padding: 10px 20px; overflow: auto; margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 14px; clear: both; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">sudo</span> <span style=\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">yum</span> update\n</pre></div><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（2）安装依赖的包</p><div style=\"background: rgb(239, 255, 244); border: 0px solid rgb(147, 147, 147); padding: 10px 20px; overflow: auto; margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 14px; clear: both; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">sudo</span> <span style=\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">yum</span> <span style=\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">install</span> curl-devel expat-devel gettext-devel openssl-devel zlib-devel <span style=\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">gcc</span> <span style=\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">perl</span>-ExtUtils-MakeMaker\n</pre></div><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（3）下载git源码并解压缩</p><div style=\"background: rgb(239, 255, 244); border: 0px solid rgb(147, 147, 147); padding: 10px 20px; overflow: auto; margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 14px; clear: both; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 14px;\">\n$ <span style=\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">wget</span> https:<span style=\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 128, 0);\">//</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 128, 0);\">github.com/git/git/archive/v2.3.0.zip</span>\n$ <span style=\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">unzip</span> v2.<span style=\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(128, 0, 128);\">3.0</span>.<span style=\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">zip</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\n$ cd git</span>-<span style=\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(128, 0, 128);\">2.3</span>.<span style=\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(128, 0, 128);\">0</span></pre></div><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（4）编译安装</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">将其安装在“/usr/local/git”目录下。</p><div style=\"background: rgb(239, 255, 244); border: 0px solid rgb(147, 147, 147); padding: 10px 20px; overflow: auto; margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 14px; clear: both; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">make</span> prefix=/usr/local/<span style=\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">git all\n</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">sudo</span> <span style=\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">make</span> prefix=/usr/local/git <span style=\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">install</span></pre></div><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（5）此时你如果使用git --version 查看git版本的话，发现git仍然是1.7.1版本。这是因为它默认使用了&quot;/usr/bin&quot;下的git。</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">你可以用下面的命令查看git所在的路径：</p><div style=\"background: rgb(239, 255, 244); border: 0px solid rgb(147, 147, 147); padding: 10px 20px; overflow: auto; margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 14px; clear: both; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 14px;\">\n$ <span style=\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">whereis</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> git\ngit: </span>/usr/bin/git /usr/local/git /usr/share/<span style=\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">man</span>/man1/git.<span style=\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(128, 0, 128);\">1</span>.gz\n</pre></div><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（6）我们要把编译安装的git路径放到环境变量里，让它替换&quot;/usr/bin&quot;下的git。为此我们可以修改“/etc/profile”文件（或者/etc/bashrc文件）。</p><div style=\"background: rgb(239, 255, 244); border: 0px solid rgb(147, 147, 147); padding: 10px 20px; overflow: auto; margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 14px; clear: both; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">sudo</span> vim /etc/profile\n</pre></div><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">然后在文件的最后一行，添加下面的内容，然后保存退出。</p><div style=\"background: rgb(239, 255, 244); border: 0px solid rgb(147, 147, 147); padding: 10px 20px; overflow: auto; margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 14px; clear: both; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 14px;\">\nexport PATH=/usr/local/git/bin:$PATH\n</pre></div><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（7）使用source命令应用修改。</p><div style=\"background: rgb(239, 255, 244); border: 0px solid rgb(147, 147, 147); padding: 10px 20px; overflow: auto; margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 14px; clear: both; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 14px;\">\nsource /etc/profile\n</pre></div><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（8）然后再次使用git --version 查看git版本，发现输出2.3.0，表明安装成功。</p><h1 style=\"margin: 10px 0px; font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2. 设置Git</h1><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（1）设置用户名和email。</p><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\ngit config --global user.name &quot;Your Name&quot;\ngit config --global user.email &quot;youremail@domain.com&quot;\n</pre><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">此时，Home目录下会新建一个.gitconfig文件</p><h1 style=\"margin: 10px 0px; font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3. 为GitHub账号添加SSH Keys</h1><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">以公钥认证方式访问SSH协议的Git服务器时无需输入口令，而且更安全。（访问HTTP协议的Git服务器时，比如提交修改，每次都需要输入口令。）</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（1）创建SSH key</p><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n$ ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &quot;youremail@163.com&quot;\n</pre><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">系统会提示key的保存位置（一般是~/.ssh目录）和指定口令，保持默认，连续三次回车即可。</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（2）Copy SSH Key</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">然后用vim打开该文件，id_rsa.pub文件内的内容，粘帖到github帐号管理的添加SSH key界面中。</p><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\nvim ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub\n</pre><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（3）添加到GitHub</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">登录github-&gt; Accounting settings图标-&gt; SSH key-&gt; Add SSH key-&gt; 填写SSH key的名称（可以起一个自己容易区分的），然后将拷贝的~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub文件内容粘帖-&gt; add key”按钮添加。</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（4）测试</p><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\nssh -T <a href=\"mailto:git@github.com\" style=\"color: rgb(70, 70, 70); text-decoration: none;\">git@github.com</a></pre><h1 style=\"margin: 10px 0px; font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4. 为GitHub上的Repository提交修改</h1><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（1）git clone已存在GitHub上的Repository。（在新建的~/MyTestFolder目录中）</p><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\ngit clone https://github.com/zhchnchn/ZhchnchnTest.git\n</pre><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（2）修改一个文件，然后提交</p><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\nvim README.md\ngit status\ngit add README.md\ngit status\ngit commit -m &quot;Edit by WorkUbuntu 1204&quot;\ngit status\ngit remote add origin https://github.com/zhchnchn/ZhchnchnTest.git\n</pre><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这时会报错误：</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">fatal: remote origin already exists.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">解决办法【3】：</p><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n$ git remote rm origin\n</pre><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">然后再次执行 git remote add origin https://github.com/zhchnchn/ZhchnchnTest.git</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（3）之后，需要将修改push到GitHub上</p><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\ngit push -u origin master\n</pre><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">执行该条命令后，会要求输入GitHub账户的用户名和密码。</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（4）提交完成后，查看GitHub上的Repository，会发现内容修改成功。</p><h1 style=\"margin: 10px 0px; font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Refer</h1><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">【1】How To Install Git on Ubuntu 14.04（<a href=\"https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-install-git-on-ubuntu-14-04%EF%BC%89\" style=\"color: rgb(70, 70, 70); text-decoration: none;\">https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-install-git-on-ubuntu-14-04）</a></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">【2】Installing Latest version of git in ubuntu（<a href=\"http://stackoverflow.com/questions/19109542/installing-latest-version-of-git-in-ubuntu%EF%BC%89\" style=\"color: rgb(70, 70, 70); text-decoration: none;\">http://stackoverflow.com/questions/19109542/installing-latest-version-of-git-in-ubuntu）</a></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">【3】Ubuntu12.04下安装Git（<a href=\"http://blog.csdn.net/biosd/article/details/9115837\" style=\"color: rgb(70, 70, 70); text-decoration: none;\">http://blog.csdn.net/biosd/article/details/9115837</a>）</p><div style=\"margin: 10px auto; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><div>【4】CentOS6.6源码安装git-2.3.0（http://blog.csdn.net/goritcly/article/details/43878209）（http://www.centoscn.com/image-text/install/2015/0225/4735.html）</div></div></div></div>"
    }
  ]
}